        this function is used to dispatch informations extracted from files and to set to default the Date field
        Parameters:
        birthdateField - : Graphic componant input text field, the user can change the value of this field
        patientList - : Graphic list componant displaying the informations from the patient objects existing in arrayPatient
        examinationList - : Graphic list componant displaying the informations from the Examen objects existing in arrayExamination
        switchRoomAndExaminationList - : Graphic list componant switching display informations between Examen objects and Chambre object
        arrayExamination - : used to keep the Examen object extracted from external file or created by the user
        arrayPatient - : used to keep the Patient object extracted from external file or created by the user
        arrayRoom - : used to keep the Chambre object extracted from external file
        examinationDateField - : Graphic componant input text field, the user can change the value of this field
        listOfBookedRoom - : Graphic list componant displaying the informations from the booked Chambre object extracted from external file or booked by the user

      • setDefaultRangeForBookingRoomDate

        public static void setDefaultRangeForBookingRoomDate(com.toedter.calendar.JDateChooser entryDateField,
                                                     com.toedter.calendar.JDateChooser releaseDateField,
                                                     Examen examination)
        This function is used to set an available range for the Chambre's entry and release date
        The minimum selectable entryDate for booking a room is put at today and it's maximum selectable entryDate is fixed at the examinationDate it constrains the user to select a date in a certain available range The minimum selectable releaseDate is set ad the examinationDate and has no further limits
        Parameters:
        entryDateField - : Graphic componant input text field, the user can change the value of this field
        releaseDateField - : Graphic componant input text field, the user can change the value of this field
        examination - : Examen Object extracted from arrayExamination and used in RoomFunction
        See Also:
        ParseFunctions.dateFormating(com.toedter.calendar.JDateChooser)
